    "description": "The LCB224 is a LED bar with 224 pieces SMD RGB LEDs. The LEDs are divided in 16 separately controllable sections, with each section having its own RGB colour setting in DMX mode. While using the fixture in stand-alone mode there are pre-programmed shows runs automatically or sound activated, pick from pre-programmed automatic programs or create your own mixture of colours in RGB mode. The extra IEC output enables you to simply link the power of multiple units together into a single socket.",
